Teasy is committed to ensuring a safe and respectful platform for all users.
We have a zero-tolerance policy for any content or behavior that involves child sexual abuse, exploitation, or endangerment.

1. Prohibited Content

The following are strictly forbidden on Teasy:

Any sexual or suggestive content involving minors.

Images, videos, or text that depict, promote, or normalize child sexual exploitation.

Attempts to solicit, groom, or exploit minors in any way.

Links, usernames, or profile details that refer to CSAE material.

2. Enforcement and Reporting

Teasy uses automated detection and human moderation to identify and remove illegal content.

Any detected CSAE content or accounts are immediately suspended and reported to relevant authorities.

Users can report violations directly in the app or by emailing safety@teasyapp.com
.

3. Cooperation with Authorities

We fully cooperate with law enforcement agencies and child protection organizations to ensure offenders are reported and prosecuted.

4. Education and Prevention

Teasy promotes awareness of online safety and responsible behavior.
We periodically remind users of community standards and enforce compliance.
